## Key Differences from CScreeningResource.addScreening

| Aspect | CScreeningResource | CScreeningReportResource |
|--------|-------------------|--------------------------|
| **Purpose** | Create new screening order | Receive screening results |
| **Direction** | Outbound (HireRight → Vendor) | Inbound (Vendor → HireRight) |
| **Request Body** | CScreeningRequest (structured) | Raw XML payload |
| **Processing** | Synchronous order creation | Asynchronous message queuing |
| **Creates** | COrder, CApplicant, COrderService | CMessage for processing |
| **Transaction ID** | Generated during request | Retrieved from payload |

